title: ApexLimit
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

An Apex item grants a bonus to an ability score only the first time it's invested within a 24-hour period, and you can benefit from only one at a time. If you invest an apex item when you already have one invested, you don't gain the ability score increase, but you do gain any other benefits.